					"value": "Dialog with the ghost of Kerri Evenfield, now freed from Oskar's body and hells-bent on taking him to the afterlife with her. She's incandescent with angry, but if the player successfully calms her anger, they can hear her explanation of her recent suicide, and get her to leave peacefully. Otherwise, they end up in combat."
				}
			}
		}
	}
